28:52.600 --> 28:53.800
Unless you want to.

28:54.100 --> 28:56.800
Uh, no, you know,
i ju-- I just figured,

28:56.800 --> 28:58.800
For the character,
for nikki heat--

28:58.800 --> 29:01.000
Yeah, you-- I think--
I think understand nikki heat

29:01.000 --> 29:03.000
Better than you think
i do.

29:07.100 --> 29:09.000
Be careful, okay?

29:11.800 --> 29:14.300
Do i detect actual concern
for my well-Being?

29:14.300 --> 29:15.900
Screw this up,
and i'll kill you.

29:16.500 --> 29:17.900
That's more like it.

29:22.600 --> 29:26.100
Okay, i have eyes
on the target. Over.

29:26.600 --> 29:27.600
Are you reading me?

29:27.600 --> 29:28.800
We don't have to
read you.

29:28.800 --> 29:31.300
We can see you.
Now shut up and focus.

29:31.500 --> 29:33.500
Roger that.
Five by five.

29:34.100 --> 29:35.400
He's quite a guy.

29:35.600 --> 29:37.300
If he only knew how big
a fan you really are.

29:37.300 --> 29:39.400
Yeah, well,
he's not going to know.

29:41.600 --> 29:44.000
You never told him how you
stood in line for an hour

29:44.000 --> 29:45.500
Just to get
your book signed...

29:47.300 --> 29:50.200
How his novels got you
through your mother's death?

29:51.000 --> 29:52.700
Is there anything
you don't remember?

29:54.000 --> 29:55.500
Not when it
comes to you.

30:07.300 --> 30:11.500
I feel like michael finding
the gun taped behind the toilet.

30:12.100 --> 30:13.100
Uh...

30:14.300 --> 30:17.600
You might want to tell ryan
and esposito to hang back.

30:17.600 --> 30:20.300
